,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":112895,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Eve: 在全国范围确实是外娶大于外嫁，但是在清华后者几乎没有","timestamp":1605081412,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":541280,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Francis","permissions":["report"],"pid":112895,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re 洞主: ","timestamp":1605081714,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":541321,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Grace","permissions":["report"],"pid":112895,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"南方很多找东南亚老婆的","timestamp":1605082467,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":541331,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Hans","permissions":["report"],"pid":112895,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"令人作呕","timestamp":1605082612,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":541407,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Isabella","permissions":["report"],"pid":112895,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"？？什么思维","timestamp":1605083733,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":541481,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Jason","permissions":["report"],"pid":112895,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"我确实想喷这个EZG，太恶心了","timestamp":1605084671,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":541735,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Kate","permissions":["report"],"pid":112895,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"新清搞这么一个案例出来，在目前普遍右转的语境下面，真的是要么蠢要么坏","timestamp":1605088226,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":541737,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Kate","permissions":["report"],"pid":112895,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"打错了  是清新","timestamp":1605088249,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":542070,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Louis","permissions":["report"],"pid":112895,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Kate: 那么发表这样的案例在未右转的语境下是否正常呢？如果是正常的，那么问题究竟出在媒体，还是出在整体右转的舆论环境呢？","timestamp":1605094133,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":542101,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Margaret","permissions":["report"],"pid":112895,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Louis: 赞同这个发问。","timestamp":1605094661,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":542257,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Kate","permissions":["report"],"pid":112895,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Louis: 我认为造成右转的原因在于国际大环境和中国目前所处的发展阶段，需要这种民族主义力量（或者说排外）来凝聚人心，所以我认为问题出在媒体","timestamp":1605096934,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":542528,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Louis","permissions":["report"],"pid":112895,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Kate: 然而到了现在必须靠排外来凝聚人心，这条路是不是本来就走歪了呢？","timestamp":1605100760,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":542544,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Kate","permissions":["report"],"pid":112895,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Louis: 虽然不能让所有人都理解和支持，但这应该是团结尽量多力量的最简单方式了，川建国不也是这么做的吗","timestamp":1605101000,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":542670,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Louis","permissions":["report"],"pid":112895,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Kate: 但历史经验告诉我们，短期的最简单往往要在长期付出代价，用排外的方式构造团结，在长远来看往往会带来更大的分裂和仇恨。而且，如果完全抛弃理想，只追求现实的短期目的，那我们与我们的对手又有什么区别呢？","timestamp":1605103275,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":542969,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Kate","permissions":["report"],"pid":112895,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Louis: 目前\u0008中国经济军事水平还不够强大，这种思潮只是权宜之计吧，之后怎么改变再从长计议","timestamp":1605107220,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":544623,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Margaret","permissions":["report"],"pid":112895,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Kate: 确认一下所以纳粹德国的右转倾向也是无可非议的吗（不是杠 单纯想知道具体标准如何区分）","timestamp":1605151095,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":545538,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Kate","permissions":["report"],"pid":112895,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Margaret: 确实值得思考，我认为纳粹过于的右了，但就怎么界定而言也不好下一个结论，cz认为每个时代都有每个时代的政治主旋律，冷战之后的趋势是朝左的，但目前因为各种原因，总体是越来越右了","timestamp":1605166441,"type":"text","url":""}],"post":{"attention":false,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"likenum":11,"permissions":["report","fold"],"pid":112895,"reply":26,"tag":null,"text":"清新时报今天发的那个“异国恋”是什么意思…用个例代替统计数据来美化巴基斯坦等第三世界国家，普遍保留着封建时期价值观的男人吗？尤其是在另几个事例中的男方都各种有规划有行动，努力为两人的未来奔波的时候，在这个事例里却强调巴男“没有规划”，“约会迟到”但是两人还希望继续在一起，这难道不是在强化东亚男性“供养者贝塔男”的固有标签，合理化国女对外国人光环的追求吗？\n我甚至有些怀疑这个案例后面有某些组织，希望通过引入移民的方式来毁坏我国国民的国家认同和民族认同","timestamp":1605080890,"type":"text","updated_at":1606782642,"url":"","vote":{}}}